articles.title: ENG vs AUS Highlights, World Cup: AUS win by 33 runs, knock ENG out of World Cup - Hindustan Times
articles.description: England vs Australia Highlights, Cricket World Cup 2023: Australia (286) beat defending champions England (253) by 33 runs to knock them out of the tournament
